data.description: Welcome to this inviting home in tranquil Summerville, No HOA. Located in the desirable Dorchester II School District, this low-maintenance sanctuary offers comfort and convenience. With a nature view and spacious layout, this 1643sqft residence is perfect for families seeking tranquility. Gather around the cozy fireplace or enjoy outdoor activities in the large backyard. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home provides practical living space. The well-appointed kitchen with luxury vinyl plank floors, dishwasher, and smooth-top range offers style and functionality. The beautiful lawn, stunning fence, and deck provide additional outdoor living space. Located in the sought-after Dorchester II neighborhood, enjoy easy access to all that Summerville has to offer.
